1. Introduction:

SoulEngine-Undertale-Template. This template is created using the LOVE2D (LOVE) engine. Template Author: CI_END.

This template aims to provide a foundation for those transitioning from Create Your Frisk (Unitale), allowing them to explore and get familiar with the new engine. For those who haven’t used the aforementioned CYF (Unitale) engine, don’t worry, we’ve also prepared general tutorials for you.

2. How to use this document:

Most sections are comprehensive tutorials on specific topics. To explore any particular area, simply open the corresponding file.